Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 11:42:31 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] feat: live diagram routes (/live, /live/:schemaId)

Serve schema JSONs from a mounted volume via Nginx and auto-import
them into the browser IndexedDB on page load, with multi-schema support.

Base: upstream chartdb/chartdb v1.20.1 (c24936a)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
